I was wrong. Isn't that enough?

00:01:58.600 --> 00:01:59.460
You're just...

00:01:59.509 --> 00:02:00.230
you...

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.750
What are all your names?

00:02:08.750 --> 00:02:09.729
My name is Laifu.

00:02:09.750 --> 00:02:10.840
My name is Huhu.

00:02:10.870 --> 00:02:11.800
My name is Jixiang.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:12.930
My name is Longlong.

00:02:13.630 --> 00:02:15.520
My little brother is called Dabao.

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:17.280
Why are these all boys' names?

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:19.000
Ms. Yi,

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.140
I'm sorry for the embarrassment.

00:02:21.829 --> 00:02:23.060
My husband Arun

00:02:23.090 --> 00:02:24.340
is an honest man

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:26.120
with no opinions of his own.

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:28.030
He listens to my mother-in-law.

00:02:28.190 --> 00:02:29.280
My mother-in-law

00:02:29.380 --> 00:02:31.440
won't stop until she gets a grandson.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.430
But

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:36.000
I had four girls one after another.

00:02:37.660 --> 00:02:39.390
When it came to the fifth child,

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:40.870
I finally had a boy.

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:44.150
My figure

00:02:44.220 --> 00:02:46.079
has changed because of childbirth,

00:02:46.079 --> 00:02:47.810
and it still hasn't recovered.

00:02:48.079 --> 00:02:50.280
It gave me all sorts of health problems.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:52.430
This is their

00:02:52.430 --> 00:02:54.290
first time visiting the factory.

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:55.210
Laifu,

00:02:55.430 --> 00:02:57.690
who told you to bring your siblings here?

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:01.080
I'm sorry for the embarrassment, Ms. Yi.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.190
It's alright.

00:03:05.910 --> 00:03:07.310
Auntie has some fish-skin peanuts here.

00:03:07.310 --> 00:03:07.870
Here.

00:03:07.870 --> 00:03:09.080
Take these and share with your sisters.

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:10.410
- Thank you. - Thank you.

00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:11.560
Thank you, Auntie.

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.150
Thank you.

00:03:21.310 --> 00:03:22.000
Ms. Su,

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:25.260
do you know why Qing and I argued?

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:30.400
All the conflicts between Qing and me

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:32.030
are because of my identity.

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:34.420
I am her sister-in-law

00:03:35.070 --> 00:03:37.000
and also a martyr's family member.

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:39.010
But no one considers that

00:03:39.010 --> 00:03:40.680
beyond these identities,

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:41.930
I am just myself.

00:03:42.430 --> 00:03:44.690
I have privacy that I don't want to share.

00:03:45.310 --> 00:03:46.190
Sometimes I just want to

00:03:46.190 --> 00:03:48.030
find a quiet corner to be alone.

00:03:49.710 --> 00:03:50.800
But everyone's

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:53.430
constant and overwhelming concern

00:03:53.940 --> 00:03:55.400
makes me feel suffocated.

00:03:56.190 --> 00:03:57.630
It makes me feel exposed

00:03:57.990 --> 00:03:59.320
and judged by everyone.

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.000
Ms. Su,

00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:05.780
I'm not targeting you.

00:04:06.190 --> 00:04:08.050
I don't expect you to understand.

00:04:08.110 --> 00:04:09.520
I'm just talking.

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:10.840
I do understand.

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.840
The fact that you're sharing this with me

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:14.150
means a lot to me.

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:17.310
You telling me about your situation

00:04:17.310 --> 00:04:18.640
also touches me deeply.

00:04:24.510 --> 00:04:26.040
Auntie, I'm hungry.

00:04:26.060 --> 00:04:27.190
It'll be ready soon.

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:28.750
Laifu is hungry too.

00:04:29.070 --> 00:04:30.250
Huhu is hungry too.

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:31.600
Jixiang is hungry too.

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.750
Dabao is hungry too.

00:04:34.430 --> 00:04:35.240
You all...

00:04:35.670 --> 00:04:37.310
I don't have enough noodles here.

00:04:37.310 --> 00:04:38.159
How about this?

00:04:38.159 --> 00:04:39.090
Let's go out to eat.

00:04:39.090 --> 00:04:39.850
My treat.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.560
Go out to eat?

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.790
Ms. Yi...

00:04:45.159 --> 00:04:46.310
Thank you then.

00:04:46.310 --> 00:04:47.409
You're welcome. Let's go.

00:04:47.409 --> 00:04:48.600
Come, give it to auntie.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:49.130
Let's go.

00:04:49.300 --> 00:04:50.390
Let's eat out.

00:04:51.510 --> 00:04:52.070
Come on.

00:04:54.190 --> 00:04:55.430
Time to go out for dinner.

00:04:55.430 --> 00:04:56.120
Let's go.

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:01.070
It's raining so hard.

00:05:01.070 --> 00:05:02.510
Should we take shelter?

00:05:02.830 --> 00:05:04.240
Let it pour. It's refreshing.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:05.190
Let's keep going.

00:05:05.190 --> 00:05:07.160
Give me back my hat.

00:05:07.190 --> 00:05:07.750
Here.

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:09.310
Take it.

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.400
Hurry.

00:05:19.320 --> 00:05:20.520
You're finally back.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.300
Where have you been?

00:05:23.630 --> 00:05:25.040
I've been looking for you everywhere,

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.920
all over the place.

00:05:27.050 --> 00:05:27.730
You.

00:05:27.750 --> 00:05:29.550
Look at you, you're soaking wet.

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:31.480
Why are you still angry?

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:32.430
Alright.

00:05:33.159 --> 00:05:33.960
Don't bother.

00:05:34.420 --> 00:05:35.750
You're running a fever.

00:05:36.270 --> 00:05:37.930
Change your clothes quickly.

00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:39.750
Come on, don't be angry.

00:05:40.390 --> 00:05:41.560
It's not a big deal.

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:42.420
You're just...

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:45.560
Just go back.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:47.270
Let me tell you something.

00:05:47.270 --> 00:05:48.400
We've been partners

00:05:48.510 --> 00:05:49.560
for over ten years.

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:51.690
I finally figured it out on my way here.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:54.200
You never kept anything from me before.

00:05:54.630 --> 00:05:56.240
Even when you had an abscess in your ass,

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:57.770
you were afraid of surgery.

00:05:57.860 --> 00:05:58.830
You told me first,

00:05:58.830 --> 00:06:00.030
not your wife.

00:06:00.830 --> 00:06:01.950
But now?

00:06:02.530 --> 00:06:04.330
You're keeping secrets from me.

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:06.750
You are hiding things from me.

00:06:06.750 --> 00:06:08.880
How many things are you hiding from me?

00:06:09.480 --> 00:06:11.210
If you don't come clean with me,

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.480
we're done for good.

00:06:13.970 --> 00:06:15.900
I have nothing to hide from you.

00:06:16.390 --> 00:06:17.750
Open the door.

00:06:17.950 --> 00:06:18.830
Just go away.

00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:21.510
Why did you lock the door? Open up!

00:06:21.510 --> 00:06:23.120
I'll tell you everything.

00:06:26.040 --> 00:06:27.310
Just open the door!

00:06:35.650 --> 00:06:37.240
Change your clothes first!

00:06:39.940 --> 00:06:40.800
Stubborn fool.

00:07:07.310 --> 00:07:07.980
Yi,

00:07:08.420 --> 00:07:08.940
hurry,

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:10.510
come with me.

00:07:11.610 --> 00:07:12.610
Come on, hurry up!

00:07:17.830 --> 00:07:19.230
Secretary Zhao, what...

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:29.950
Sister,

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:31.830
Sister, find the key to the second floor,

00:07:31.830 --> 00:07:32.190
quickly!

00:07:32.190 --> 00:07:32.600
Okay.

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:33.270
Go now!

00:07:33.290 --> 00:07:34.220
Secretary Zhao,

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.800
why did you bring me here?

00:07:37.250 --> 00:07:38.170
Wen is dying.

00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:50.870
Wen.

00:07:52.030 --> 00:07:52.640
Wen.

00:07:54.870 --> 00:07:55.950
Look who's here.

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:03.950
Minister Wen.

00:08:12.190 --> 00:08:13.040
You're here.

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:18.020
As soon as you arrived,

00:08:18.310 --> 00:08:19.440
he came back to life.

00:08:20.190 --> 00:08:22.360
It's fine. You don't need to do anything.

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:23.360
Just stay here.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.820
That's the best medicine.

00:08:28.870 --> 00:08:29.530
Yi,

00:08:30.270 --> 00:08:31.560
take good care of him.

00:09:44.470 --> 00:09:45.470
Don't leave.

00:09:48.740 --> 00:09:49.550
I won't.

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:34.750
Sister.

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:35.840
Coming.

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:36.550
Sister.

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:38.790
Who is it?

00:10:40.860 --> 00:10:42.480
How is he? You took him to the hospital?

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:43.510
Hospital? No need.

00:10:43.510 --> 00:10:45.170
Why are you here, Sister Fang?

00:10:45.550 --> 00:10:47.270
He's fine. He is in good hands.

00:10:47.660 --> 00:10:49.060
Good hands?

00:10:49.510 --> 00:10:50.320
Who?

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:53.080
We can't let unreliable people walk in.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:54.540
Reliable, very reliable.

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:56.720
What's not reliable about it?

00:10:57.090 --> 00:10:59.180
They're both willing.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:01.080
Don't worry about it.

00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:05.670
Zhao Hangong, what are you thinking?

00:11:06.750 --> 00:11:09.080
They're not together anymore.

00:11:09.270 --> 00:11:11.270
Zhou introduced Yi Yi to someone.

00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:12.960
They're getting along well.

00:11:13.150 --> 00:11:14.600
I'm looking for someone suitable

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.440
for Wen.

00:11:15.440 --> 00:11:17.390
Why are you trying to push them together?

00:11:17.390 --> 00:11:18.200
I'm not pushing them together.

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:19.200
You really have nothing better to do.

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:20.630
They both want this.

00:11:20.630 --> 00:11:21.790
Let's not worry about it.

00:11:21.790 --> 00:11:22.480
Besides...

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:23.740
you don't understand.

00:11:23.790 --> 00:11:25.080
What don't I understand?

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:26.790
I introduced you to your wife!

00:11:26.790 --> 00:11:27.360
That's true.

00:11:27.360 --> 00:11:28.360
When you first met Jiang,

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.390
you couldn't even speak.

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:30.510
You kept running to the bathroom.

00:11:30.510 --> 00:11:31.840
And you say I don't understand?

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:33.750
Stop talking about my embarrassing past.

00:11:33.750 --> 00:11:34.600
Alright, Sister.

00:11:34.600 --> 00:11:35.840
Let's stop worrying about this, okay?

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:36.510
Be quiet.

00:11:36.910 --> 00:11:38.840
Is this just my personal business?

00:11:39.280 --> 00:11:39.750
I...

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:40.530
Get out!

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:42.910
Sister.

00:11:43.140 --> 00:11:44.660
Save him some face.

00:11:45.630 --> 00:11:46.390
Sister.

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:53.850
Come out.

00:11:55.910 --> 00:11:56.720
Come out.

00:12:04.340 --> 00:12:05.640
Zhao Hangong, go home.

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:11.860
Close the door.

00:12:31.390 --> 00:12:33.960
Didn't I make myself clear the other day?

00:12:34.510 --> 00:12:36.570
I told you to go home and think it over.

00:12:38.150 --> 00:12:39.460
You don't understand

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:41.750
what kind of man he is.

00:12:42.440 --> 00:12:44.370
You two are completely different.

00:12:45.080 --> 00:12:47.320
Although he used to be an intellectual,

00:12:47.790 --> 00:12:49.840
he's been in the army for over ten years.

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:52.440
He's been through blood and fire.

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:56.270
He's not the bookish scholar you think.

00:12:57.270 --> 00:12:59.910
He was once a military commander.

00:13:00.630 --> 00:13:02.560
Do you understand what that means?

00:13:04.360 --> 00:13:06.000
You don't understand at all.

00:13:06.510 --> 00:13:07.970
Have you thought about it?

00:13:08.170 --> 00:13:09.170
Once you two are together,

00:13:09.170 --> 00:13:11.120
what kind of life will you face?

00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:13.120
Minister Wen is a leader.

00:13:13.120 --> 00:13:15.320
He will always prioritize his work.

00:13:16.270 --> 00:13:17.750
He can't give you romance.

00:13:18.080 --> 00:13:19.750
He can't give you poetry and art.

00:13:19.750 --> 00:13:22.000
And he can't satisfy your fantasies.

00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:24.500
This surely isn't the life you want.

00:13:24.530 --> 00:13:26.480
Then what kind of life do I want?

00:13:26.620 --> 00:13:27.640
I certainly know.

00:13:28.030 --> 00:13:29.440
But I can tell you this.

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:32.600
Minister Wen absolutely cannot give you.

00:13:32.630 --> 00:13:34.510
I've never expected anyone

00:13:34.540 --> 00:13:36.060
to provide the life I want.

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:38.340
How do you define your relation with him?

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:39.910
I respect Minister Wen.

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:42.150
I enjoy talking with him.

00:13:42.510 --> 00:13:44.200
Even seeing him, hearing him speak

00:13:44.200 --> 00:13:46.480
is a sophisticated pleasure.

00:13:46.790 --> 00:13:48.320
I won't depend on anyone.

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:49.960
Nor do I ask for anything.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.150
I have my own life.

00:13:51.150 --> 00:13:52.510
I have my own work.

00:13:52.640 --> 00:13:54.540
Stop beating around the bush. Just say it.

00:13:54.540 --> 00:13:56.670
Do you want to form a family with him?

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:02.720
Fine.

00:14:04.240 --> 00:14:05.600
If you insist that I take a stand,

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:06.510
I'll tell you.

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:10.270
I like Minister Wen.

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:13.390
I want to live with him.

00:14:28.800 --> 00:14:30.120
I want to be with her.

00:14:41.030 --> 00:14:41.600
Okay.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:42.730
Alright.

00:14:43.670 --> 00:14:45.320
Okay, Wen Pu.

00:14:45.670 --> 00:14:46.790
Fine, Wen Pu.

