Then we'll follow the regulations.

00:14:51.510 --> 00:14:52.670
The organization must conduct

00:14:52.670 --> 00:14:54.670
a thorough background check on her.

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:57.360
Before the investigation results come out,

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.150
you two cannot meet.

00:15:03.910 --> 00:15:05.840
You're thinking too simply.

00:15:44.320 --> 00:15:46.520
I'm sorry for putting you through this.

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:53.630
Don't be.

00:15:55.510 --> 00:15:56.390
It's good

00:15:57.420 --> 00:15:58.420
like this.

