You worry about government policy changes,

00:17:44.750 --> 00:17:47.350
and you also try to exploit loopholes to

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:49.720
corrupt officials and seek private gain.

00:17:49.720 --> 00:17:51.570
No, absolutely not.

00:17:52.070 --> 00:17:53.070
I suggest you

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:54.330
go back and

00:17:54.640 --> 00:17:55.920
read more books, read more newspapers,

00:17:55.920 --> 00:17:57.470
and study Central Government's directives.

00:17:57.470 --> 00:17:58.270
Yes.

00:17:58.550 --> 00:18:00.480
We won't forget those

00:18:00.630 --> 00:18:01.690
who once helped us.

